{"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview\/dequeuereusableannotationviewwithidentifier:"]}],"metadata":{"symbolKind":"method","roleHeading":"Instance Method","externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNMapView(im)dequeueReusableAnnotationViewWithIdentifier:","role":"symbol","title":"dequeueReusableAnnotationViewWithIdentifier:","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"dequeueReusableAnnotationViewWithIdentifier:","kind":"identifier"}],"remoteSource":{"fileName":"MLNMapView.h","url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNMapView.h#L1879"},"fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"dequeueReusableAnnotationViewWithIdentifier:","kind":"identifier"}]},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView"]]},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Returns a reusable annotation view object associated with its identifier."}],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"text":"- (","kind":"text"},{"text":"MLNAnnotationView","kind":"typeIdentifier","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)MLNAnnotationView"},{"text":" *) ","kind":"text"},{"text":"dequeueReusableAnnotationViewWithIdentifier:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"NSString","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSString"},{"text":" *) ","kind":"text"},{"text":"identifier","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"platforms":["iOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"parameters":[{"name":"identifier","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"A string identifying the annotation view to be reused.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"This string is the same one you specify when initially returning the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"annotation view object using the ","type":"text"},{"code":"-mapView:viewForAnnotation:","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" method.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"kind":"parameters"},{"content":[{"level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"return-value","text":"Return Value"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"An annotation view object with the given identifier, or "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"nil"},{"type":"text","text":" if no"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"such object exists in the reuse queue."}]}],"kind":"content"},{"content":[{"text":"Discussion","type":"heading","anchor":"discussion","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"For performance reasons, you should generally reuse ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"objects for identical-looking annotations in your map views. Dequeueing","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"saves time and memory during performance-critical operations such as","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"scrolling.","type":"text"}]}],"kind":"content"}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView\/dequeueReusableAnnotationViewWithIdentifier:","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"kind":"symbol","sections":[],"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapView":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView","title":"MLNMapView","role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"MLNMapView","kind":"identifier"}],"abstract":[{"text":"An interactive, customizable map view with an interface similar to the one","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"provided by Apple’s MapKit.","type":"text"}],"type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotation":{"role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotation","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNAnnotation"}],"title":"MLNAnnotation","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" protocol is used to provide annotation-related information"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to a map view. To use this protocol, you adopt it in any custom objects that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"store or represent annotation data. Each object then serves as the source of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"information about a single map annotation and provides critical information,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"such as the annotation’s location on the map. Annotation objects do not provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the visual representation of the annotation but typically coordinate (in"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"conjunction with the map view’s delegate) the creation of an appropriate"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"objects to handle the display."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","type":"topic","kind":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapView/dequeueReusableAnnotationViewWithIdentifier:":{"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview\/dequeuereusableannotationviewwithidentifier:","title":"dequeueReusableAnnotationViewWithIdentifier:","type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Returns a reusable annotation view object associated with its identifier."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView\/dequeueReusableAnnotationViewWithIdentifier:","role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"dequeueReusableAnnotationViewWithIdentifier:"}],"fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"- "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"dequeueReusableAnnotationViewWithIdentifier:"}],"kind":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotationView":{"fragments":[{"text":"MLNAnnotationView","kind":"identifier"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationview","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView","role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView"},{"text":" class is responsible for marking a point annotation","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"with a view. Annotation views represent an annotation object, which is an","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"object that corresponds to the ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation"},{"text":" protocol. When an annotation’s","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"geographic coordinate is visible in the map view, the map view asks its","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"delegate to a corresponding annotation view. If an annotation view is created","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"with a reuse identifier, the map view may recycle the view when it goes","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"offscreen.","type":"text"}],"title":"MLNAnnotationView","type":"topic"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"role":"collection","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","title":"MapLibre","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling.","type":"text"}],"type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre"}}}